      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="8177066c-01bc-4341-9cf5-8d210c2367a5" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Bộ khuếch đại</Vi>
          <En>A device that increases the amplitude of a signal, especially in audio systems to boost sound volume.</En>
          <Example>The guitarist plugged his electric guitar into a tube amplifier to get a richer tone.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="836aea0c-ca66-4bd2-ab46-7a06c847b25f">
              <Vi>Sử dụng trong phòng thu âm hoặc trên sân khấu để tăng cường âm thanh.</Vi>
              <En>Used in recording studios or live performances to increase sound volume and clarity.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="9934ab24-eb89-4770-8213-c2d579037958">
              <Vi>Một bộ khuếch đại có thể được tích hợp trong loa hoặc là thiết bị độc lập.</Vi>
              <En>An amplifier may be built into a speaker or exist as a standalone unit.</En>
